# Tailwind CSS v4 Configuration

## Font Configuration

This project uses **Tailwind CSS v4** with **Fontsource** for self-hosted fonts.

### Font Setup

**Fonts are imported in [main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx):**

```tsx
import '@fontsource/poppins'
import '@fontsource/dynapuff'
```

**Fonts are configured in [index.css](mdc:src/index.css) using `@theme`:**

```css
@import 'tailwindcss';

@theme {
  --font-dyna: 'DynaPuff', cursive;
  --font-sans: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}
```

### Usage in Components

Use the `font-{name}` utility class (without the "family" part):

```tsx
<h1 className='font-dyna'>Title</h1>
<p className='font-sans'>Body text</p>
```

## Breaking Changes from v3

### Deprecated Classes

- ❌ `flex-grow-*` → ✅ `grow-*`
- ❌ `flex-shrink-*` → ✅ `shrink-0`
- ❌ `decoration-clone` → ✅ `box-decoration-clone`
- ❌ `decoration-slice` → ✅ `box-decoration-slice`
- ❌ `overflow-ellipsis` → ✅ `text-ellipsis`
- ❌ `outline-none` → ✅ `outline-hidden`
- ❌ `text-opacity-*` → ✅ `text-{color}/{opacity}` (e.g., `text-blue-500/50`)

### Ring Utility

Default ring width changed from `3px` to `1px`:

```tsx
/* For 3px ring, explicitly specify */
className = 'ring-3 ring-blue-500'
```

### Syntax Changes

**Variables in arbitrary values:**

```tsx
/* v3 */
className = 'bg-[--brand-color]'

/* v4 */
className = 'bg-(--brand-color)'
```

## Configuration Pattern

### Adding New Fonts

1. Install Fontsource package:

   ```bash
   pnpm install @fontsource/{font-name}
   ```

2. Import in [main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx):

   ```tsx
   import '@fontsource/{font-name}'
   ```

3. Add to `@theme` in [index.css](mdc:src/index.css):

   ```css
   @theme {
     --font-{name}: '{FontName}', fallback;
   }
   ```

4. Use in components:
   ```tsx
   <div className='font-{name}'>Text</div>
   ```

### Custom Theme Variables

Define custom theme tokens using `@theme` in CSS:

```css
@theme {
  /* Colors */
  --color-primary: #3b82f6;

  /* Fonts */
  --font-custom: 'Custom Font', sans-serif;

  /* Spacing */
  --spacing-custom: 2rem;

  /* Breakpoints */
  --breakpoint-custom: 1200px;
}
```

## Development Tips

- **Performance:** Tailwind v4 is 5x faster for full builds
- **Configuration:** No JavaScript config file needed
- **Imports:** Use `@import 'tailwindcss'` instead of `@tailwind` directives
- **Fonts:** All fonts are self-hosted via Fontsource for better privacy and performance
